What makes a good workout shoe for men?

Good workout shoes generally feature a mesh upper to increase airflow during wear. Shoes with mesh panels or perforations help to keep your feet cool during your workout.

What are the best shoes for playing indoor sports?

If you are playing sports like basketball at the gym, you ll want a shoe with a durable rubber outsole that won t scuff the court. Having a sturdy rubber bottom will help you maintain traction and not slip.

What makes a good work shoe?

If you are working in a rugged environment, we recommend selecting a durable boot with a thick rubber outsole. The high-cut design on most boots will help to protect your ankle and add stability.
